<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 03:35:01 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a448ae104c95</link><description>&lt;p&gt;人和高尔夫球车火车桥&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A paved path leads under a rustic bridge surrounded by dense green foliage, opening into a bright grassy field beyond." height="3425" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/6a448ae104c95.jpg" width="4567"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 03:35:01 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a448a9ca6083</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从3号洞往下看的画面，背景是明尼阿波利斯的天际线。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A lush green golf course is framed by dense trees, revealing a hazy city skyline in the distance beneath a pale, overcast sky." height="2385" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/6a448a9ca6083.jpg" width="3179"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 03:33:52 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4459f0de769</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在约塞米蒂国家公园闲逛。真是个不可思议的地方！约塞米蒂瀑布巨大而美丽。如果你仔细观察，可以看到上下两段瀑布。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Cloudless sky above, huge granite cliffs, and meadow below. Upper right of cliffs is a large waterfall (1,430 ft) and lower left is a smaller waterfall (320 ft)." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dcr/6a4459f0de769.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dcr.some.pics"&gt;@dcr&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 00:06:12 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4457098a5d8</lin